{
  "stem": "9723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when you send a letter, they-- they-- there was no-- no return address on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I imagine that this was secret enough so she wouldn't find out where I-- where I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, a couple of weeks later, I just go out, and there she is, with a-- walking with the Polish colonel down the path.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I guess she met somebody who happened to be Jew-- a Jew, a colonel in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he uh-- they were friends during that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he managed to locate me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So uh, I don't-- I don't know how or why she agreed that I would stay in the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she let me stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- she didn't object.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess she knew that-- that-- that I was stubborn enough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I wanted to run away, I'd run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this way, they assured her-- they assured her, I guess, that I was in really no immediate danger.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not on the front lines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, this was true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the Russians, I suppose, wanted to make sure that the Polish army would not get decimated during the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they made sure that they were really not included in the very heavy fighting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So most of them would survive when-- when the war was over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's-- that was the-- that was the case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I stayed in the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They got a tailor, made me a uniform that fit and got me a pair of boots that fit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And uh, I actually performed the duties of a soldier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was promoted to corporal eventually, and learned the Morse code.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I uh, took and sent messages, so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
